General.Name: Vate Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: Vate Technology Co., Ltd. provides integrated circuit (IC) testing services in Taiwan and China. The company offers IC testing services related to the service of wafer probing and final testing; BURN IN, a test service on electrical components and final products; and LED products. It also provides chip probing test, final test, SLT system module test, CMOS image sensor testing, and back end services, as well as sells LED panel light products. Vate Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 1977 and is based in Hsinchu City, Taiwan.
